## About This Collection

This article features 50+ tested Midjourney prompt templates to help you quickly generate high-quality images in various styles.

## Photography Style Templates

### Portrait Photography
Template: `portrait of [subject], soft lighting, bokeh background, 85mm lens, f/1.4 --ar 3:4`

### Landscape Photography
Template: `landscape of [scene], golden hour, dramatic clouds, wide angle --ar 16:9`

## Illustration Style Templates

### Flat Illustration
Template: `flat illustration of [subject], minimal, pastel colors, clean lines --ar 1:1`

### Watercolor Style
Template: `watercolor painting of [subject], soft edges, flowing colors, artistic --ar 4:3`

## 3D Style Templates

### Isometric View
Template: `isometric view of [subject], 3D render, soft shadows, pastel palette --ar 1:1`

## Usage Tips

1. Replace `[subject]` with your desired topic
2. Adjust the aspect ratio parameter `--ar` as needed
3. Add `--v 6` to use the latest version
4. Use `--style raw` for a more natural look
